    "The magnified images in Fig. 5k-m show that the FCN-32s captured relatively globally rough defect features.",
    "In contrast, in that order, the U-Net, FCN-8s, and FCN-16s identified more detailed defect objects, as seen in the region (III) in Fig. 3c.",
